<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhōng xīn chuán yáng zhǔ de míng 迦南309</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ nǐ gěi wǒ men lì xià yǒng yuǎn bù biàn de yuē, nǐ de xìn shí shàng dá qióng cāng,
 nǐ de ēn diǎn xiàng tiān shàng de xīng shù bù qīng, wǒ ruò shù diǎn bǐ hǎi shā gèng duō.
 wèi rén lèi shě mìng yòu jiù le wǒ men de mìng, wǒ men yòng shén me lái bào dá nǐ?
 zhǐ yǒu zǒu guò yuǎn shān yuǎn shuǐ, tà biàn yì xiāng yì zú, zhōng xīn chuán yáng nǐ de shèng míng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>309</hymn_number>
</song>